{
  "stem": "22652.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I was disappointed, I just missed de Gaulle's speech.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I-- I had hoped to hear him speak.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, well, you know, the word de Gaulle kept being heard in the convent.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everybody talked about him, and that he was going to be there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I think we read it in the paper.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Well, I-- you know, I can't-- I don't remember the specific.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But it was a big thing, de Gaulle being the liberator.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so knowing that, I look forward to hear him speak.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And by the time we got to the public place, where the defile, the parade, was going through, he had finished his speech, and the crowd was dismantling.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then we saw the Allies, the Americans, and the Allies, and the French Resistance parading in the streets.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And, and the war, for us, the war was over.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And people were dancing in the streets.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And Americans were throwing chewing gum, and candy, and chocolate, and soap all over the place.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I think, if I remember correctly, there-- one of the punishment for women who have collaborated or who had had love affairs with Nazis or German soldiers, they-- their head was shaven and a swastika was painted on their head.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It seemed as if they took all their hatred and made them their scapegoat.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I remember those women being dragged through the streets and spit upon.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I remember kind of an uneasy feeling about it all.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I remember that-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] A feeling, mixed emotions, [SOBBING] that the war was finally over.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "This was the day we all had waited for and a feeling of uncertainty.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I was 12, 13 then.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I didn't know what would come next.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
